<div class="content" name="CAPROPVARIANT" uuid="40a8da49-ff56-4dee-bc99-b96e520f896c"><p>The CAPROPVARIANT structure defines a counted array of <a href="195c9807-7377-4617-9a1b-b6da6ccebf52" data-linktype="relative-path">PROPVARIANT (section 2.2.13.2)</a>
values.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct tagCAPROPVARIANT {
   unsigned long cElems;
   [size_is(cElems )] PROPVARIANT* pElems;
 } CAPROPVARIANT;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>cElems:</b>  MUST be set to the total
number of elements of the array.</p><p><b>pElems:</b>  An array of
PROPVARIANT (section 2.2.13.2) values.</p></div>